{
  "stem": "22979.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But this, this journey on the train from Loslau to Ravensbruck, that was the worst experience what I ever had, freezing to death, throwing over my dead comrades who survived three years in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And finally we arrived about to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "That was a women's camp, which from where we saw in Auschwitz the first day when we came, the thousand inmates from Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And the camp was full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We didn't have room where even to sit outside because that was, you know, the only camps which were still in the German Reich.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The rest were already liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This part was liberated by the Russian armies, where we came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it was so full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We didn't have, you know, a little space well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But they built a big tent there, where thousands and thousands of inmates from camps from Poland and Germany came there where it drove us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Still, you know, they took us with them, the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And my friends with whom we survived and I were sitting outside the tent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We thought that was the last minutes of our lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "No food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And still, other inmates were pouring in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "So then I, I think we squeezed in somewhere to the tent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "It was, you know, full of mud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But we were sitting on the floor anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "No windows there then, just the tent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we got, I think-- so one day, a day later, we had to line up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought kettles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were pushing so hard to these kettles, the kettles turned over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in front of the tent was the frozen, I mean, soil.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was like glass, shiny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The food poured outside, and the food was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what we did?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
